      "description": "Offered is a mechanically peerless example of analog precision. This specimen features a high-revving, naturally aspirated power plant with individual throttle bodies that provide instantaneous transient response. The valvetrain and variable timing systems are dialed to factory specifications, ensuring a linear power delivery across the entire tachometer. The chassis remains structurally flawless, exhibiting zero subframe fatigue and retaining its original suspension kinematics for optimal lateral load management. Power is delivered through a crisp-shifting manual gearbox to a robust limited-slip differential, with no play in the drivetrain. This vehicle is a concours-level survivor, free of oxidation and preserved in a state of mechanical stasis.",
